---
title: Grilled Shawarma Chicken and Golden Rice with Cucumber Salad and Spicy Tahini Sauce
description: Fire up your grill and clear your schedule to enjoy this Middle Eastern-inspired recipe. Golden rice, studded with sweet peppers is the base to smoky grilled shawarma-spiced chicken, generously drizzled with an unexpectedly addicting spicy tahini sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1007_W29_CA_RC23736-1_MAIN_R_low-bca58418.jpg
